aq3sq1"><div class=3D"ed4x0bn0 css-48o5u4 e1m4c3o81"><div class=3D"textBloc=
k"><p>The compression ratio is a characteristic of <strong>combustion engin=
es</strong> (and, surprisingly, has nothing to do with file compression). I=
